title: College football: Washington stops USC 17-12
text:
Photo: Jae C. Hong, Associated Press USC’s Steve Sarkisian checks the scoreboard after a Washington touchdown. USC’s Steve Sarkisian checks the scoreboard after a Washington...
Myles Gaskin ran for 134 yards and a fourth-quarter touchdown, and visiting Washington shut down No. 17 USC’s high-powered offense in a 17-12 victory over the Trojans on Thursday night.
